{"tid":2084544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國外交部：「香港自治法案」 只是廢紙一張　警告不得審議","createTime":"2020-06-29T09:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T11:04:13.000Z","uid":212626,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"65a4a94413bf29d6815098902c3d2795d00565b6","tid":2084544,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部強調，中方堅決反對美國參議院通過「香港自治法案」，已向美方提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n發言人趙立堅說，中方敦促美方認清形勢，立即停止以任何方式干涉香港事務和中國內政，<span style=\"color: red;\">不得審議、推進和實施有關涉港消極議案，更不得以此為由對中方進行所謂制裁</span>，否則中方將採取堅決有力的應對和反制措施，一切後果完全由美方承擔。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅又說，無論亂港分裂勢力如何叫囂，無論外部反華勢力如何施壓，都阻擋不了中方推進香港國安立法的決心和行動，他們的圖謀必將失敗，有關議案也是廢紙一張。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534716-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534716-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=c18a4130\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534716-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b64197dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534716-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c985f46e174bb77aa958f0ed630ff01479cb67f","tid":2084544,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加速主義"},{"pid":"e51dcddc6ef62d03462b21cfb75634faa29aaf3f","tid":2084544,"uid":2746,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pBnePd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pBnePd.gif&h=d1d0a7c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c2ccc03e07fa82236d19e105f1c80bc0b8942fe","tid":2084544,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl